## Token Hygiene Rules
- Omit unchanged files entirely — only show diffs or the modified function
- Collapse boilerplate (imports, config) unless it's the subject of the change
- Never re-explain a concept already established in this session
- If asked to refactor, output only the affected section + a summary of what changed

## Input Discipline
- These rules themselves are kept under 40 lines to minimize input tax
- Prefer inline comments over prose explanations in code
